      "text": "Good morning입니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 50.26,
      "end": 55.54,
      "text": "There are many dogs like trouble in our real life, 그렇죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 57.36,
      "end": 57.78,
      "text": "Are there?"
    },
    {
      "start": 57.96,
      "end": 59.66,
      "text": "Yeah, 특히 무슨 의미냐면"
    },
    {
      "start": 59.66,
      "end": 62.42,
      "text": "The dogs that inherit fortune"
    },
    {
      "start": 62.42,
      "end": 64.3,
      "text": "Yeah, from their owners"
    },
    {
      "start": 64.3,
      "end": 65.38,
      "text": "Rich, lucky dogs"
    },
    {
      "start": 65.38,
      "end": 66.62,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah, yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 66.62,
      "end": 67.66,
      "text": "And what about cats?"
    },
    {
      "start": 68.12,
      "end": 69.88,
      "text": "그런 고양이들도 혹시 있을까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 70.02,
      "end": 71.74,
      "text": "We're going to talk about cats now"
    },
    {
      "start": 71.74,
      "end": 77.12,
      "text": "원래 주로 강아지들 중에서 유산을 많이 상속받는 경우는"
    },
    {
      "start": 77.12,
      "end": 78.5,
      "text": "종종 접할 수가 있는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 78.5,
      "end": 81.66,
      "text": "고양이들도 과연 있을지 궁금한데요"
    },
    {
      "start": 81.66,
      "end": 83.22,
      "text": "Well, I looked it up"
    },
    {
      "start": 83.22,
      "end": 84.52,
      "text": "and there is a cat"
    },
    {
      "start": 84.52,
      "end": 86.6,
      "text": "a very wealthy cat"
    },
    {
      "start": 86.6,
      "end": 87.94,
      "text": "named Blackie"
    },
    {
      "start": 87.94,
      "end": 88.66,
      "text": "Blackie"
    },
    {
      "start": 88.66,
      "end": 92.5,
      "text": "considered the richest cat by Guinness World Records"
    },
    {
      "start": 92.5,
      "end": 93.98,
      "text": "until 2018"
    },
    {
      "start": 93.98,
      "end": 96.2,
      "text": "So I guess that record was broken"
    },
    {
      "start": 96.2,
      "end": 97.94,
      "text": "There's an even richer cat now"
    },
    {
      "start": 97.94,
      "end": 98.72,
      "text": "Yeah, I think so"
    },
    {
      "start": 98.72,
      "end": 103.0,
      "text": "But this cat inherited a 12.5 million dollar fortune"
    },
    {
      "start": 103.0,
      "end": 104.78,
      "text": "That's a lot of money"
    },
    {
      "start": 104.78,
      "end": 106.78,
      "text": "한 140억이라는 건가요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 106.86,
      "end": 107.68,
      "text": "그 정도예요"
    },
    {
      "start": 107.68,
      "end": 110.44,
      "text": "네, 140억의 어마어마한 돈"
    },
    {
      "start": 110.44,
      "end": 112.56,
      "text": "And his owner"
    },
    {
      "start": 112.56,
      "end": 112.86,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 112.86,
      "end": 114.38,
      "text": "Or he or she, I'm not sure"
    },
    {
      "start": 114.38,
      "end": 115.7,
      "text": "Ben Ria"
    },
    {
      "start": 115.7,
      "end": 116.12,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 116.12,
      "end": 117.62,
      "text": "From the UK, England"
    },
    {
      "start": 117.62,
      "end": 119.38,
      "text": "He died in May 1988"
    },
    {
      "start": 119.38,
      "end": 124.4,
      "text": "And he left a 7 million pound fortune to Blackie"
    },
    {
      "start": 124.4,
      "end": 126.36,
      "text": "So pounds, that is"
    },
    {
      "start": 126.36,
      "end": 128.02,
      "text": "I mean, dollars, 12.5 million"
    },
    {
      "start": 128.02,
      "end": 129.18,
      "text": "그래서 140억"
    },
    {
      "start": 129.18,
      "end": 131.9,
      "text": "Yeah, actually this guy, this owner"
    },
    {
      "start": 131.9,
      "end": 132.98,
      "text": "was a cat person"
    },
    {
      "start": 132.98,
      "end": 134.58,
      "text": "He was crazy about cats"
    },
    {
      "start": 134.58,
      "end": 134.92,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 134.92,
      "end": 138.02,
      "text": "So he shared his huge mansion with 15 cats"
    },
    {
      "start": 138.02,
      "end": 141.66,
      "text": "And this Blackie was the last surviving cat"
    },
    {
      "start": 141.66,
      "end": 143.24,
      "text": "The rest had passed away"
    },
    {
      "start": 143.24,
      "end": 146.16,
      "text": "So he's like, he didn't have a lot of family"
    },
    {
      "start": 146.3,
      "end": 147.72,
      "text": "He only had a few friends"
    },
    {
      "start": 147.72,
      "end": 149.52,
      "text": "He was kind of eccentric"
    },
    {
      "start": 149.52,
      "end": 152.48,
      "text": "So he left a lot of money to his cat"
    },
    {
      "start": 152.48,
      "end": 154.5,
      "text": "And then he donated some money"
    },
    {
      "start": 154.5,
      "end": 155.7,
      "text": "To charities"
    },
    {
      "start": 155.7,
      "end": 159.0,
      "text": "And then he gave some cash to his gardener"
    },
    {
      "start": 159.0,
      "end": 159.96,
      "text": "His mechanic"
    },
    {
      "start": 159.96,
      "end": 160.98,
      "text": "And his plumber"
    },
    {
      "start": 160.98,
      "end": 163.2,
      "text": "So the guys who worked in his house"
    },
    {
      "start": 163.2,
      "end": 163.56,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 163.56,
      "end": 164.2,
      "text": "That's nice"
    },
    {
      "start": 164.2,
      "end": 164.86,
      "text": "Wow"
    },
    {
      "start": 164.86,
      "end": 166.68,
      "text": "And he also gave a house to a friend"
    },
    {
      "start": 166.68,
      "end": 167.78,
      "text": "One friend"
    },
    {
      "start": 167.78,
      "end": 168.1,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 168.1,
      "end": 171.1,
      "text": "So that was how he divided up his wealth"
    },
    {
      "start": 171.1,
      "end": 171.68,
      "text": "Wow"
    },
    {
      "start": 171.68,
      "end": 174.48,
      "text": "쭉 듣다 보니까 이런 생각이 났어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 174.48,
      "end": 177.82,
      "text": "So there were the ones who were the closest to him"
    },
    {
      "start": 177.82,
      "end": 179.54,
      "text": "Before he died"
    },
    {
      "start": 179.54,
      "end": 180.04,
      "text": "Yes"
    },
    {
      "start": 180.04,
      "end": 185.06,
      "text": "His cat, his plumber, his mechanic, his gardener, and one friend"
    },
    {
      "start": 185.06,
      "end": 192.7,
      "text": "모두 다 자신이 죽기 전에 그때까지 가장 가까이 있었던 이들인 것 같습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 192.7,
      "end": 198.92,
      "text": "사람들만 있는 것이 아니라 이와 같이 고양이한테도 해당이 된 상황인 거죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 198.92,
      "end": 200.1,
      "text": "아, 예"
    },
    {
      "start": 200.1,
      "end": 201.28,
      "text": "우리 딸들"
    },
    {
      "start": 201.28,
      "end": 202.7,
      "text": "아빠랑 친하게 지내야 돼요"
    },
    {
      "start": 202.7,
      "end": 204.66,
      "text": "친하게 지내야"
    },
    {
      "start": 204.66,
      "end": 205.66,
      "text": "또 그렇게 가나요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 206.24,
      "end": 207.54,
      "text": "아, just joking인데"
    },
    {
      "start": 207.54,
      "end": 208.48,
      "text": "뭐"
    },
    {
      "start": 208.48,
      "end": 209.82,
      "text": "친하지 못해요"
    },
    {
      "start": 209.82,
      "end": 210.36,
      "text": "Good idea"
    },
    {
      "start": 210.36,
      "end": 212.28,
      "text": "이런 거 해야죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 212.28,
      "end": 212.54,
      "text": "네"
    },
    {
      "start": 212.54,
      "end": 212.8,
      "text": "네"
    },
    {
      "start": 212.8,
      "end": 213.48,
      "text": "네"
    },
    {
      "start": 213.48,
      "end": 215.48,
      "text": "오늘 장면 확인해 볼게요"
    },
    {
      "start": 215.48,
      "end": 220.3,
      "text": "I had to work three jobs just to save up and strike out on my own"
    },
    {
      "start": 220.3,
      "end": 222.56,
      "text": "Something my parents did not want me to do, by the way"
    },
    {
      "start": 222.56,
      "end": 223.54,
      "text": "Why don't you be a doctor?"
    },
    {
      "start": 223.78,
      "end": 224.44,
      "text": "Or a teacher?"
    },
    {
      "start": 224.6,
      "end": 226.48,
      "text": "How are you ever going to survive as a singer?"
    },
    {
      "start": 226.96,
      "end": 228.06,
      "text": "Anyway, there were arguments"
    },
    {
      "start": 228.06,
      "end": 229.68,
      "text": "There were hurt feelings"
    },
    {
      "start": 229.68,
      "end": 231.24,
      "text": "And now I'm here all alone"
    },
    {
      "start": 231.24,
      "end": 233.0,
      "text": "Not feeling particularly confident"
    },
    {
      "start": 233.0,
      "end": 237.88,
      "text": "음, 그래도 이 조가 has a good personality"
    },
    {
      "start": 237.88,
      "end": 239.18,
      "text": "한 것 같아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 239.18,
      "end": 243.02,
      "text": "I mean, she just adopted a dog from the middle of the street"
    },
    {
      "start": 243.02,
      "end": 243.4,
      "text": "네"
    },
    {
      "start": 243.4,
      "end": 248.36,
      "text": "그래서 어저께는 얘가 바깥에 놓여 있었잖아요, trouble이"
    },
    {
      "start": 248.36,
      "end": 249.02,
      "text": "네"
    },
    {
      "start": 249.02,
      "end": 251.14,
      "text": "She let him in again"
    },
    {
      "start": 251.14,
      "end": 252.28,
      "text": "She felt bad?"
    },
    {
      "start": 252.48,
      "end": 252.74,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 252.74,
      "end": 253.48,
      "text": "She felt sorry"
    },
    {
      "start": 253.48,
      "end": 253.8,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 253.8,
      "end": 254.7,
      "text": "It was freezing cold"
    },
    {
      "start": 254.7,
      "end": 256.16,
      "text": "She's warm hearted, right?"
    },
    {
      "start": 256.58,
      "end": 257.52,
      "text": "그러면서 이제"
    },
    {
      "start": 257.52,
      "end": 259.22,
      "text": "She told her tail"
    },
    {
      "start": 259.22,
      "end": 264.78,
      "text": "그녀에 대한 어렸을 때부터 있었던 스토리를 이야기를 해주고 있습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 264.78,
      "end": 266.6,
      "text": "Ah, her personal story"
    },
    {
      "start": 266.6,
      "end": 267.06,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 267.06,
      "end": 272.44,
      "text": "그러면서 이제 이 이야기를 들으면서 우리의 트러블도"
    },
    {
      "start": 272.44,
      "end": 275.08,
      "text": "어쩌면 he's getting to know life"
    },
    {
      "start": 275.08,
      "end": 275.52,
      "text": "그렇죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 275.8,
      "end": 277.94,
      "text": "인생을 배우는 거 아니겠습니까?"
    },
    {
      "start": 277.94,
      "end": 281.86,
      "text": "Life, I mean, trouble lived in a hole, a bubble"
    },
    {
      "start": 281.86,
      "end": 286.06,
      "text": "And he does not know about, you know, having a tough life"
    },
    {
      "start": 286.06,
      "end": 286.34,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 286.34,
      "end": 288.08,
      "text": "Or just a tough upbringing"
    },
    {
      "start": 288.08,
      "end": 291.94,
      "text": "So Zoe and the other dogs are teaching him"
    },
    {
      "start": 291.94,
      "end": 292.32,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 292.32,
      "end": 293.42,
      "text": "Slowly, bit by bit"
    },
    {
      "start": 293.42,
      "end": 294.68,
      "text": "Now he's in real life"
    },
    {
      "start": 294.68,
      "end": 296.26,
      "text": "This is reality"
    },
    {
      "start": 296.26,
      "end": 296.74,
      "text": "그렇죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 296.74,
      "end": 297.68,
      "text": "Face reality"
    },
    {
      "start": 297.68,
      "end": 300.0,
      "text": "네, 중요한 표현들 먼저 알려주세요"
    },
    {
      "start": 300.0,
      "end": 302.34,
      "text": "Strike out on my own"
    },
    {
      "start": 302.34,
      "end": 303.96,
      "text": "Strike out"
    },
    {
      "start": 303.96,
      "end": 305.52,
      "text": "라는 표현이 들렸는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 305.52,
      "end": 307.7,
      "text": "Strike out"
    },
    {
      "start": 307.7,
      "end": 309.74,
      "text": "혼자 힘으로 라는 거"
    },
    {
      "start": 309.74,
      "end": 313.36,
      "text": "혹은 독립하다 라는 동사적으로도 쓰일 수가 있고요"
    },
    {
      "start": 313.36,
      "end": 315.22,
      "text": "또 야구에서도 쓰이잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 315.22,
      "end": 316.0,
      "text": "Strike out"
    },
    {
      "start": 316.0,
      "end": 319.2,
      "text": "Yeah, strike out 하면 독립 생각 안 하고"
    },
    {
      "start": 319.2,
      "end": 320.44,
      "text": "바로 야구"
    },
    {
      "start": 320.44,
      "end": 322.5,
      "text": "Oh, I striked him out"
    },
    {
      "start": 322.5,
      "end": 324.7,
      "text": "Three strikes, three strikeouts"
    },
    {
      "start": 324.7,
      "end": 326.16,
      "text": "아, 삼진 아웃"
    },
    {
      "start": 326.16,
      "end": 326.44,
      "text": "그렇죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 326.96,
      "end": 327.9,
      "text": "Three strikes"
    },
    {
      "start": 327.9,
      "end": 329.82,
      "text": "그거 three strikes and you're out"
    },
    {
      "start": 329.82,
      "end": 332.1,
      "text": "아, 삼진 아웃, strike out"
    },
    {
      "start": 332.1,
      "end": 335.8,
      "text": "If you have three strikeouts in a row, then you go up to bat"
    },
    {
      "start": 335.8,
      "end": 337.2,
      "text": "Change"
    },
    {
      "start": 337.2,
      "end": 340.2,
      "text": "그래요, 지금 야구를 좋아하시는 우리 청취자분들도"
    },
    {
      "start": 340.2,
      "end": 342.12,
      "text": "갑자기 눈이 번쩍 뜨이셨을 겁니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 342.12,
      "end": 346.42,
      "text": "그런데 오늘은 strike out on my own이라고 해서"
    },
    {
      "start": 346.42,
      "end": 349.12,
      "text": "혼자 힘으로 살아남다"
    },
    {
      "start": 349.76,
      "end": 353.6,
      "text": "혼자 힘으로 독립하다 라는 의미로 해석하시면 되겠어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 353.6,
      "end": 355.96,
      "text": "I'm here all alone"
    },
    {
      "start": 355.96,
      "end": 358.02,
      "text": "I'm here all alone"
    },
    {
      "start": 358.02,
      "end": 360.02,
      "text": "마치 어떤 가사인 것 같아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 360.02,
      "end": 362.94,
      "text": "그래서 난 지금 여기 혼자 있네"
    },
    {
      "start": 362.94,
      "end": 364.02,
      "text": "이것도 괜찮겠죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 364.02,
      "end": 365.5,
      "text": "I'm here all alone"
    },
    {
      "start": 365.5,
      "end": 367.1,
      "text": "I'm here all alone"
    },
    {
      "start": 367.1,
      "end": 367.8,
      "text": "덩그러니"
    },
    {
      "start": 367.8,
      "end": 369.92,
      "text": "좋은 표현이에요"
    },
