    {
      "start": 668.45,
      "end": 669.31,
      "text": "이 트러블이"
    },
    {
      "start": 669.31,
      "end": 670.75,
      "text": "맥앤치즈를 찾을"
    },
    {
      "start": 670.75,
      "end": 671.77,
      "text": "상황이 아니라는 거죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 671.77,
      "end": 673.11,
      "text": "I mean, she's doing"
    },
    {
      "start": 673.11,
      "end": 674.85,
      "text": "She's working as a pizza delivery girl"
    },
    {
      "start": 674.85,
      "end": 676.47,
      "text": "She's trying to become a singer"
    },
    {
      "start": 676.47,
      "end": 678.15,
      "text": "She's behind on her rent"
    },
    {
      "start": 678.15,
      "end": 681.57,
      "text": "Her landlord threatened to evict her"
    },
    {
      "start": 681.57,
      "end": 683.71,
      "text": "She's facing a lot of troubles"
    },
    {
      "start": 683.71,
      "end": 685.61,
      "text": "사면 조가네요, 그죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 685.85,
      "end": 686.13,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 686.13,
      "end": 688.07,
      "text": "이 장면 한 번 더 들어보죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 688.07,
      "end": 690.3,
      "text": "I had to work three jobs"
    },
    {
      "start": 690.3,
      "end": 691.36,
      "text": "just to save up"
    },
    {
      "start": 691.36,
      "end": 692.66,
      "text": "and strike out on my own"
    },
    {
      "start": 692.66,
      "end": 693.58,
      "text": "Something my parents"
    },
    {
      "start": 693.58,
      "end": 694.9,
      "text": "did not want me to do, by the way"
    },
    {
      "start": 694.9,
      "end": 695.88,
      "text": "Why don't you be a doctor"
    },
    {
      "start": 695.88,
      "end": 696.76,
      "text": "or a teacher"
    },
    {
      "start": 696.76,
      "end": 698.2,
      "text": "How are you ever gonna survive"
    },
    {
      "start": 698.2,
      "end": 698.82,
      "text": "as a singer?"
    },
    {
      "start": 699.32,
      "end": 700.4,
      "text": "Anyway, there were arguments"
    },
    {
      "start": 700.4,
      "end": 702.02,
      "text": "there were hurt feelings"
    },
    {
      "start": 702.02,
      "end": 703.58,
      "text": "and now I'm here all alone"
    },
    {
      "start": 703.58,
      "end": 705.38,
      "text": "Not feeling particularly confident"
    },
    {
      "start": 705.38,
      "end": 707.46,
      "text": "오, 네"
    },
    {
      "start": 707.46,
      "end": 709.56,
      "text": "6841님께서"
    },
    {
      "start": 709.56,
      "end": 711.46,
      "text": "구수하당 크리스"
    },
    {
      "start": 711.46,
      "end": 713.14,
      "text": "이렇게 보내주셨네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 713.14,
      "end": 713.86,
      "text": "구수하네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 713.86,
      "end": 714.3,
      "text": "네"
    },
    {
      "start": 714.3,
      "end": 716.48,
      "text": "어찌나 구수한 용어들을"
    },
    {
      "start": 716.48,
      "end": 717.78,
      "text": "많이 이야기를 하시는지"
    },
    {
      "start": 717.78,
      "end": 719.38,
      "text": "아주 깨알 재미가 있습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 719.38,
      "end": 720.98,
      "text": "아, 저희도 영어도"
    },
    {
      "start": 720.98,
      "end": 722.28,
      "text": "구수하게 해봅시다"
    },
    {
      "start": 722.28,
      "end": 723.54,
      "text": "아우, 기대할게요"
    },
    {
      "start": 723.54,
      "end": 724.46,
      "text": "우리 다음 주"
    },
    {
      "start": 724.46,
      "end": 725.38,
      "text": "스크린 잉글리시"
    },
    {
      "start": 725.38,
      "end": 726.76,
      "text": "구수하게 잘 부탁드립니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 726.76,
      "end": 727.12,
      "text": "네"
    },
    {
      "start": 727.12,
      "end": 728.46,
      "text": "잘 부탁드립니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 728.46,
      "end": 729.4,
      "text": "네, 다음 주에 만나요"
    },
    {
      "start": 729.4,
      "end": 730.42,
      "text": "See you next week"
    }
  ]
}